<span id="freeTextContainer3936540451586778911">Well, hello there, Mr. Ichabod Crane! I cannot believe I waited so long before meeting you.<br/><br/><img src='https://images.gr-assets.com/hostedimages/1478465205ra/21076248.gif' width='500' height='276' alt='description' class='gr-hostedUserImg'/><br/><br/>I really don&apos;t see the horror part in this classic. I found myself smiling throughout the entire story. And it was all Irving&apos;s fault. He&apos;s just so funny and charming. <br/>There was no dialogue at all. I became aware of that at some point and wandered how come I still enjoyed it.<br/><br/>The ending fit the character perfectly. I would have not wanted it any other way.<br/><br/><img src='https://images.gr-assets.com/hostedimages/1478465616ra/21076296.gif' width='500' height='230' alt='description' class='gr-hostedUserImg'/></span>
